title: New Summer Blockbuster “Terror On The Prairie”
description:
Disney canceled Gina Carano. But not for long. Her new movie, Terror On The Prairie, premieres tonight June 14th exclusively on the Daily Wire. Tune in at 8:30pm ET for the pre-show, 9pm ET for the premiere, and stick around afterwards for a Q&A. Hollywood’s loss is our gain.
